<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id" class="overflow-hidden">
<head>
    {{{head}}}
</head>
<body>
    <main class="grid max-md:grid-rows-2 md:grid-cols-[repeat(2,_1fr)] h-dvh md:pl-5 justify-between">
        <div class="pt-2 md:pt-4 md:flex justify-center flex-col w-[80%] max-md:pl-1 md:pl-6">
            <h1>Hey, Anda Adalah Yang Pertama!</h1>
            <p class="mt-4">Untuk saat ini, Site ini belum memiliki admin. Anda dapat membuat akun dan mengakses dashboard. Jangan khawatir, Anda tetap dapat membuat akun untuk admin lain melalui dashboard. </p>
            <form action="/admin/login" method="post">
                <fieldset class="mt-4 mb-2">
                    <label for="username">Username</label>
                    <input type="text" id="username" placeholder="Masukkan Username" name="username" class="my-2 max-sm:min-w-60 md:w-80">
                    <label for="password">Buat Password</label>
                    <div class="flex items-center">
                        <input type="password" id="password" placeholder="Buat Password" name="password" class="my-2 max-sm:min-w-60 md:w-80">
                        <div class="material-symbols-outlined pass-eye -translate-x-9">visibility_off</div>
                    </div>
                    <label for="confirm-password">Konfirmasi Password</label>
                    <div class="flex items-center">
                        <input type="password" id="confirm-password" placeholder="Masukkan Kembali Password" class="my-2 max-sm:min-w-60 md:w-80">
                        <div class="material-symbols-outlined pass-eye -translate-x-9">visibility_off</div>
                    </div>
                </fieldset>
                <button class="btn-primary" type="submit">Masuk</button>
            </form>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-end md:items-center justify-end w-[100%] md:h-svh">
            <img src="/asset/undraw_designer_efwz-cropped.svg" class="h-[75%]" alt="">
        </div>
    </main>
</body>
</html>